com.github.lb.stindex.spatial.sfc.tiered

Class TieredSFCIndexStrategy

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.tm.stindex.spatial.sfc.tiered.TieredSFCIndexStrategy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HierarchicalNumericIndexStrategy, IndexStrategy, NumericIndexStrategy, PartitionIndexStrategy<MultiDimensionalNumericData,MultiDimensionalNumericData>, Persistable, SortedIndexStrategy<MultiDimensionalNumericData,MultiDimensionalNumericData>

    public class TieredSFCIndexStrategy
extends java.lang.Object
implements HierarchicalNumericIndexStrategy
    This class uses multiple SpaceFillingCurve objects, one per tier, to represent a single cohesive index strategy with multiple precisions
